ACADEMIC ACKNOWLEDGMENTS

This project was developed as part of the Master's degree in Engineering and 
Ergonomics of Physical Activity (IEAP) at the University of Montpellier.

Supervisor: Antoine DUFOURNEAU

Third-party code and methodologies referenced:
- Time-Delay Embedding: Fraser & Swinney (1986), Takens (1981)
- Locomotor Resilience Metrics: Wurdeman et al. (2012), Ravi et al. (2021)
- EMD Decomposition: Huang et al. (1998)
- Python Libraries: NumPy, SciPy, Matplotlib, pandas (BSD/MIT licenses)
- R Packages: tidyverse, ggplot2, plotly (GPL/MIT licenses)
